content.description:
Near the center of Book Cliffs is a large open book, with two bolted lines on the left wall (

Guillotine

and

Blues Streak

), a broken pillar in the corner, and an attractive green face on the right wall (

Green Eggs and Ham

).  To the right of the buttress/arete formed by the right-side of the green face (

A-climb-a-tize

) is a slightly right-leaning crack leading to an obvious roof.  Climb this (some possible loose rock, but inconsequential), judiciously turn the roof, and continue up face to the top.

content.location:
Right (eastern) side of Book Cliffs, left of an obvious arete with four bolts (

Hero Maker

).
